         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Mount Gambier, ¶ SA. ¶ 6 May 1856. ¶ Esteemed Mr Krichauff, ¶  ¶ I received your letter with the enclosed £17/-/- safely, but could not reply the same evening, as the mail arrived too late. ¶  ¶ My br...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">M56.05.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Bertha Mueller to Friedrich Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Private hands.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Mt Gambier</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">Mai d 6t 1856.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Werther Herr Krichauff</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihren Brief vom 18t April mit Einlage von £17 habe ich richtig erhalten, und konnte den Abend nicht mehr antworten, weil die Post zu spät gekommen. —<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ueber die weitere Verpachtung des Landes der 40 Acker, hat mein Bruder mir keine Instructionen gegeben, — und handeln Sie daher wie es nach Ihrem Gutdünken scheint, — hoffentlich werden wir in Zukunft wenigstens 10/- pr Acker bekommen. Wenn Sie keinen Pächter bekommen können für 1 Jahr, verpachten Sie es nur ruhig auf mehrere. Ich habe vorige Woche von Melbourne gehört, dass mein Bruder seine Stelle wieder bekommen wird, sobald er returnirt und in dem Falle wird es ihm sicher lieb sein, wenn das Land verpachtet ist. — Aber handeln Sie natürlich nach ihrem eigenen Gutdünken. —<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die Stadtacker in New-Hamburg liegen No 23 und 24 — Theil von der Section 2607 in der Angas Special Survey — der Stadtacker in Tanunda No 11 — Ich bin im Besitz der Deeds<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe auch den Contract mit Herrn Stein in Händen, — Land, Haus und Fenz sind nach Verlauf der Pachtzeit in vollkommen guten Zustande abzuliefern</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Für die freundlichen Wünsche danke ich Ihnen Alle herzlich. — Dr Wehl wird mit nächster Post an Sie schreiben. Clara, Wehl u ich senden herzliche Grüsse an Sie Alle</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dass ich Unterzeichnete von Herrn Krichauff die Summe von £34 für Rente erhalten habe bescheinige ich hiermit.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Bertha Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mount Gambier</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Mai d 5t 1856</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Mount Gambier,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>SA.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6 May 1856.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Mr Krichauff,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I received your letter with the enclosed £17/-/- safely, but could not reply the same evening, as the mail arrived too late.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My brother has not given me any instructions concerning the further leasing of the 40 acres of land.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Two adjacent holdings each of 20 acre at Bugle Ranges, SA<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>(Gemmell (1975).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Proceed therefore as you think best. I hope that in future we will be able to get at least 10 shillings per acre. If you cannot find a tenant for one year, it will be alright for you to lease it for several years. I have heard from Melbourne last week, that my brother will get his position back as soon as he returns,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M was away on the North Australian Exploring Expedition under A. C. Gregory.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The source of Bertha's information is not known.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>and in that case will probably be glad, if the land has been leased. But of course you should act as you think best.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The town allotments in New-Hamburg are No 23 and 24, part of Section 2607 in the Angas Special Survey;<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn3" n="4">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>New Hamburg<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>was<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>2 km south of present-day Strathalbyn, SA; its name was changed to Willyaroo in 1916.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the town allotment in Tanunda is No 11. I have the title deeds.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I also have here the contract with Mr Stein; land, house and fence are to be handed back in good condition after the lease expires.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Thank you all very much for your kind wishes<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn4" n="5">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bertha was to marry George Doughty on 24 June.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>. Dr Wehl will write to you by the next mail. Clara, Wehl and I send our sincere regards to you all.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I herewith confirm that I the undersigned have received the sum of £34/-/- for rent from Mr Krichauff.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Bertha Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Mount Gambier</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">5th of May 1856.</p>
         </div>
